title: Adi David | Medical Massage Therapy
text:
Adi David
    Professional medical massage for healing, balance, and recovery
  




  
    Welcome
    
      My name is Adi David, a certified medical massage therapist dedicated to helping people 
      recover from pain, stress, and physical imbalances through evidence-based bodywork and personalized care.
    
    
      Each session is tailored to your unique needs — whether you’re dealing with chronic pain, muscle tension, 
      or simply looking to restore calm and well-being.
